{"type": "root", "attrs": {"icon": "FUR/groommerge", "parent": "hairtools"}, "body": [{"level": 0, "type": "title", "indent": 0, "text": ["Merge Groom Objects"], "extent": [42, 66]}, {"type": "summary", "indent": 0, "text": ["Combines the guides and skin of multiple groom objects."], "extent": [66, 130]}, {"level": 2, "id": null, "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["Overview"], "extent": [130, 145], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["It is often useful to set up a groom using separate ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/obj/guidegroom", "type": "link", "text": ["Guide\nGroom"], "fullpath": "/nodes/obj/guidegroom"}, " objects, but you usually don\u2019t want to\n", {"scheme": "Shelf", "value": "groom_animateguides", "type": "link", "text": ["animate"], "fullpath": "/shelf/groom_animateguides"}, " or ", {"scheme": "Shelf", "value": "groom_simguides", "type": "link", "text": ["simulate"], "fullpath": "/shelf/groom_simguides"}, " them\nindividually. This tool takes individual grooms from different parts of the character, and merges them together. Once they are merged, you can continue adding nodes to the single stream and not be concerned with the individual grooms anymore."], "extent": [145, 592]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/obj/guidedeform", "type": "link", "text": ["Guide Deform"], "fullpath": "/nodes/obj/guidedeform"}, ", ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/obj/guidesim", "type": "link", "text": ["Guide Simulate"], "fullpath": "/nodes/obj/guidesim"}, ", and ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/obj/hairgen", "type": "link", "text": ["Hair Generate"], "fullpath": "/nodes/obj/hairgen"}, " can operate on the output of this node, so they only have to be set up once."], "extent": [592, 780]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["This is useful for working separately on different parts of a character. Often different parts have fur of varying directions, lengths, and densities. This tool allows you to merge the separate parts together seamlessly."], "extent": [780, 1002]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["For more information, see the ", {"scheme": null, "value": "/fur/workflow", "type": "link", "text": ["Fur Workflow"], "fullpath": "/fur/workflow"}, " help."], "extent": [1002, 1068]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Image", "value": "/images/fur/merge1.jpg", "type": "img", "text": ""}, "\n", {"scheme": "Image", "value": "/images/fur/merge2.jpg", "type": "img", "text": ""}], "extent": [1068, 1131]}]}, {"level": 2, "id": "includeme", "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["Using Merge Groom Objects"], "extent": [1131, 1175], "body": [{"type": "ord_group", "body": [{"blevel": 6, "type": "ord", "indent": 4, "text": ["Click the ", {"scheme": "Icon", "value": "FUR/groommerge", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/shelf/FUR/groommerge"}, {"type": "ui", "text": ["Groom Merge"]}, " tool on the ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Hair Utils"]}, " tab."], "extent": [1175, 1262]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "ord", "indent": 4, "text": ["Select the groom objects to merge and press ", {"keys": ["Enter"], "type": "keys", "text": null}, " to confirm your selection."], "extent": [1262, 1354]}], "container": true}, {"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["For specific parameter help see the ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/obj/groommerge", "type": "link", "text": ["Groom Merge"], "fullpath": "/nodes/obj/groommerge"}, " node help."], "extent": [1354, 1440]}]}, {"type": "note_group", "body": [{"type": "note", "indent": 0, "role": "item", "extent": [1440, 1446], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/obj/guidegroom", "type": "link", "text": ["Guide Groom"], "fullpath": "/nodes/obj/guidegroom"}, " can also take any groom node, including ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/obj/groommerge", "type": "link", "text": ["Groom Merge"], "fullpath": "/nodes/obj/groommerge"}, " as input."], "extent": [1446, 1573]}], "container": true}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}, {"type": "tip_group", "body": [{"type": "tip", "indent": 0, "role": "item", "extent": [1573, 1578], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["You can add multiple ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/obj/hairgen", "type": "link", "text": ["Hair Generate"], "fullpath": "/nodes/obj/hairgen"}, " or ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/obj/guidedeform", "type": "link", "text": ["Guide Deform"], "fullpath": "/nodes/obj/guidedeform"}, " nodes after the merge to continue to work on the individual parts."], "extent": [1578, 1744]}], "container": true}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}], "title": ["Merge Groom Objects"], "summary": ["Combines the guides and skin of multiple groom objects."]}